io.scanbot.sdk.utils

Class ViewUtils.DefaultAnimationListener

  • io.scanbot.sdk.utils.ViewUtils.DefaultAnimationListener
  • Enclosing class:
    ViewUtils

    public static class ViewUtils.DefaultAnimationListener

    Implementation of Animator.AnimatorListener that does nothing. Used as base class for creating anonymous classes, which doesn't force you to override all the methods.

    Also, ensures that .onAnimationFinished will be invoked not more than once per animation (which, for instance, can be possible on HTC One X).

    See Also:
    Animator.AnimatorListener, .onAnimationFinished
